{{>alert}}

<main class="body">
    <section class="sec">
        <div class="section-content margin-center">
            <aside>
                <div class="aside-content">
                    <h3 class="intro-title">Rules for RSVP
                    </h3>
                    <br />
                    <p><strong class="p-color">* YOU MUST MAKE A RESERVATION THROUGH THIS LINK TO
                            CLAIM YOUR SLOT. RSVP until 3 days before event. WALK-INS WILL NOT BE
                            ACCEPTED.*</strong></p>
                    <br />
                    <br />

                    <p><strong class="p-color"> ** All invited guests MUST fill out an RSVP form EACH **</strong></p>
                    <br />
                    <br />

                    <p><strong class="p-color">
                            ** Due to a maximum occupancy at the space,
                            only
                            invited guests are accepted. **
                        </strong>
                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <br />

                    <p><strong class="p-color">
                            *** There is a $30.00 NON REFUNDABLE Entrance Fee
                            per person to be paid in advance by RSVP date, not at door ***
                        </strong></p>
                    <br />
                    <br />

                    <h2 style="font-weight: bold" class="text-center">MUST BRING ID
                    </h2>

                    <br />

                </div>
            </aside>

            <article>
                <h2 class="sec-titles text-left">Please fill out all the fields in this form!</h2>

                <form id="form-registration">
                    <div class="form-components">
                        <label for="form_first_name">First Name</label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="First Name" name="form_first_name" id="form-first-name"
                            class="textbox" maxlength="25"/>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-components">
                        <label for="form_last_name">Last Name</label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Last Name" name="last-name" id="form-last-name"
                            class="textbox" maxlength="25"/>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-components">
                        <label for="form_confirm_age">I am at least 21 years old and am aware I must bring a government
                            issued
                            ID to the venue on the day of the event.</label>
                        <input type="radio" name="age-consent" id="form-confirm-age" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-components">
                        <label for="form_email">Enter your email</label>
                        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" name="email" id="form-email" class="textbox" maxlength="50"/>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-components">
                        <label for="form_username">Username</label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Last Name" name="last-name" id="form-username"
                            class="textbox" maxlength="25"/>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-components">
                        <label for="form_password">Password</label>
                        <input type="password" placeholder="Last Name" name="last-name" id="form-password"
                            class="textbox" maxlength="25"/>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-components">
                        <p>Confirm attendance?</p>
                        <div>
                            <div class="attendance">
                                <input type="radio" name="form-attend" id="attend-yes" value="true" />
                                <label for="attend-yes"> Yes </label>
                            </div>

                            <div class="attendance">
                                <input type="radio" name="form-attend" id="attend-no" value="false" />
                                <label for="attend-no"> No </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    <p> "Users will be able to change their attendance choice up to a week before the event. Afterwards,
                        users
                        will NOT be able to change their answer on this form. If a user decides they cannot attend after
                        the
                        registration deadline, they must call the venue place directly and may be charged a cancellation
                        fee."
                    </p>

                    <br />

                    <p> "Guests that originally notated their attendance as 'Not Sure' will automatically be placed as
                        will not
                        attend. Any guests who RSVPs two weeks before the day of the event will be given a courtsey
                        email
                        reminding them of their selected attendance choice, therefore, giving all guests at that time an
                        opportunity to make a last minute reservation change if they choose to do so before there are 7
                        days
                        prior to the event."</p>
                    <br />


                    <div class="form-components">
                        <label for="form-terms" style="font-weight:bold">I have read the terms above and understand I
                            have the
                            right to change my
                            attendance answer up to 7 days before the event.</label>
                        <input type="radio" name="agreement" id="form-terms" />
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="highlighted-options text-center margin-center">
                        <h6>Complete RSVP</h6>
                    </button>
                </form>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<script src="/script/alert.js"></script>
<script src="/script/register.js"></script>